### 5. 并行执行 + SSE 事件

#### 新增事件类型

```ts
// types.ts
type AgentEvent =
  | { type: 'schema:skeleton'; data: { schema: PageSchema } }     // NEW: 骨架 schema
  | { type: 'schema:block:start'; data: { blockId: string; description: string } }  // NEW
  | { type: 'schema:block'; data: { blockId: string; node: SchemaNode } }  // 已有
  | { type: 'schema:done'; data: { schema: PageSchema } }         // 已有
  // ... 其他已有事件
```

#### Orchestrator 并行改造

```ts
// page-builder-orchestrator.ts（核心改动）
async function* pageBuilderOrchestrator(...) {
  // 1. Plan
  const plan = await planPage.execute({ request, context });
  yield { type: 'plan', data: plan };

  // 2. 骨架 → 立刻推送
  const skeletonSchema = buildSkeletonFromLayout(plan);
  yield { type: 'schema:skeleton', data: { schema: skeletonSchema } };

  // 3. 并行生成 blocks（max 5 并发）
  const blockResults = new Map<string, GenerateBlockResult>();
  const pending: Promise<{ blockId: string; result: GenerateBlockResult }>[] = [];
  const semaphore = createSemaphore(5);

  for (const block of plan.blocks) {
    yield { type: 'schema:block:start', data: { blockId: block.id, description: block.description } };

    pending.push(semaphore.acquire().then(async (release) => {
      try {
        const result = await generateBlock.execute({ block, request, context, pageTitle: plan.pageTitle });
        return { blockId: block.id, result };
      } finally {
        release();
      }
    }));
  }

  // 4. 竞速等待，先完成先 yield
  const remaining = new Set(pending);
  while (remaining.size > 0) {
    const completed = await Promise.race(remaining);
    remaining.delete(/* completed promise */);
    blockResults.set(completed.blockId, completed.result);
    yield { type: 'schema:block', data: { blockId: completed.blockId, node: completed.result.node } };
  }

  // 5. 最终组装
  const finalSchema = await assembleSchema.execute({ plan, blocks: [...blockResults.values()], request });
  yield { type: 'schema:done', data: { schema: finalSchema } };
}
```

> [!NOTE]
> `AsyncGenerator` 不能在 Promise 回调中 yield，上述代码为伪代码。实际实现需要用事件队列模式：block 完成时 push 到队列，主循环从队列 shift 并 yield。

#### 骨架生成

```ts
function buildSkeletonFromLayout(plan: PagePlan): PageSchema {
  // 按 layout 生成 Row/Col 骨架结构
  // 每个 block 位置放 antd Skeleton 占位节点
  const skeletonNode = (blockId: string, desc: string) => ({
    id: `${blockId}-skeleton`,
    component: 'Card',
    props: { title: desc },
    children: [{
      id: `${blockId}-skeleton-body`,
      component: 'Skeleton',  // antd Skeleton 组件
      props: { active: true, paragraph: { rows: 4 } },
    }],
  });

  // 用 assembleFromLayout 拼装，只是 blockNodes 是 skeleton
  const blockNodes = new Map(plan.blocks.map(b => [b.id, skeletonNode(b.id, b.description)]));
  return wrapInPageRoot(assembleFromLayout(plan.layout, blockNodes));
}
```

---

### 6. 前端改动

#### 页面渲染侧

```
schema:skeleton    → setSchema(skeletonSchema) → 页面立刻渲染骨架占位
schema:block       → 热替换 blockId 对应节点 → 加 fadeIn 动画
schema:done        → 全量替换最终 schema（兜底一致性）
```

热替换逻辑：深度遍历 schema tree，找到 `id === blockId + "-skeleton"` 的节点，用 block 的真实 node 替换。

#### 聊天窗口侧

```
plan               → 渲染 block 列表，每个 block 显示描述 + ⏳
schema:block:start → 对应 block 变为 🔄 生成中 (Spin)
schema:block       → 对应 block 变为 ✅ 完成
全部完成            → 列表收起或淡出
```

状态管理：`Map<blockId, 'waiting' | 'generating' | 'done'>`

